{"tid":1115107,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《戰鎚：混沌禍源》Warhammer：Chaosbane Beta 後感","createTime":"2019-04-19T02:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T07:46:06.000Z","uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8bd508998ae79baf1c5b882dab2c7b66ff3e19","tid":1115107,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/54/90ee766a1642e3a0cb987adc37147hu5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F54%2F90ee766a1642e3a0cb987adc37147hu5.JPG&h=664aec1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為有預購,收到條BETA KEY<br />\n玩咗一個鐘,升到12LV<br />\n玩法係diablo like<br />\n手感唔係太好,比同類型既grim dawn好少少<br />\n支援手掣,手掣手感好過K&amp;M<br />\n得4個職業,因為係BETA無中文,劇情都懶得睇,全部都係去唔同地方殺下怪,救下人咁<br />\n地圖設計極差,因為佢唔係一張地圖連接另一張地圖<br />\n而係係主城出去之後直接傳到你個任既地圖,基本上係無地圖設計<br />\n玩既係矮人屠夫,每個職既分別都幾大,有唔同既怒氣技同閃避技<br />\n屠夫可以拉繩閃避<br />\n有一點幾鍾意,因為屠夫既戰錘故事設定係一心求死<br />\n所以係無頭盔,無胸甲,無手套<br />\n取而代之既係換鬍鬚,紋身同臂環<br />\n目前打既怪係野獸人派系同混沌納垢教派<br />\n未見有BOSS,最勁既怪都係混沌種同呢隻肥蛆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oC67KZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoC67KZ7.jpg&h=7bdbd2c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以線上組隊<br />\nBETA過程中單機模式無彈過GAME<br />\n線上模式彈過一次<br />\n<br />\n總結:純粹鍾意diabio like既可以唔買<br />\n但鍾意中古戰錘既值得一買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253db77fcf8def8a61e684f5a7b4a4170892b2fe","tid":1115107,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee67bfa0297b4c9e5b09bacc98fdd0a84635e0d5","tid":1115107,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"253db77fcf8def8a61e684f5a7b4a4170892b2fe","tid":1115107,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime